Authorship
----------

Horizon CloudBeats is a fork of FH6 Universal Radio. The following
modifications and new features were created by MyLuxy and are
Copyright (C) 2026 MyLuxy, released under the GPLv3:

  - Spotify source support
  - Standalone desktop companion app (HorizonCloudBeats.exe)
  - Automatic dependency installer for yt-dlp, ffmpeg and deno
  - Fixed 5-band equalizer (non-functional in the original build)
  - Fixed the in-game station name; optional now-playing banner
  - Code optimizations and reliability fixes


